data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in one of Yuma's newest subdivisions. This newly built home boasts 3 bedrooms, 3 baths, and a host of luxurious features. Enjoy vaulted ceilings, modern finishes, custom stained kitchen cabinets and granite countertops all throughout. The property is a haven for outdoor enthusiasts, featuring full front landscaping, single AND double side gates. Step into a backyard oasis complete with a pergola, outdoor kitchen, convenient outside shower, and a bonus outdoor bathroom.
